                      "repsMin": 5,
                      "repsMax": 6,
                      "load": "Heavy \u2014 RPE 8 by set 3",
                      "tempo": null,
                      "notes": "Push hips back, soft knee. Feel the hamstring stretch at the bottom \u2014 that's the load, not a lower back pull. Drive hips through to stand tall. Do 1\u20132 lighter ramp-up sets before your first working set.",
                      "priority": "primary",
                      "orderIndex": 0,
                      "restSeconds": 15,
                      "alternatives": []
                    },
                    {
                      "exerciseId": "db_bench_press",
                      "sets": 3,
                      "repsMin": 6,
                      "repsMax": 8,
                      "load": "Moderate-heavy \u2014 RPE 8",
                      "tempo": null,
                      "notes": "2-second controlled descent, explosive press. Full stretch at the bottom. Superset \u2014 go directly from the RDL without sitting down.",
                      "priority": "primary",
                      "orderIndex": 1,
                      "restSeconds": 75,
                      "alternatives": []
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "name": "SQUAT + ROW",
